<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.7">
<l>valaiyuḷ ḷakappaṭut teṉṉainaṉ ṉeñcaṅ kūvikkoṇ</l>
<l>ṭalaikaṭal paḷḷi yammāṉai yāḻip pirāṉṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kalaiko ḷakalalku ṟōḻī naṅkaṇka ḷālkaṇṭu</l>
<l>talaiyil vaṇaṅka māṅkolō taiyalār muṉpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will there be bowing, on the part of the head,</l>
<l>seeing with our eyes, friend with broad hips held by a girdle,</l>
<l>the lord of the discus himself, the god whose bed is the agitated ocean, having caught me in [his] net [and] calling, taking [my] good heart,</l>
	<l>– in front of the [other] women?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
